README.md
     1→# Enclosed crypto library
     3→This package contains the natives crypto primitives used by the [Enclosed lib and project](https://enclosed.cc). It is a standalone package built to provide compatibility between different environments by exposing the same API for node:crypto and web SubtleCrypto.
     4→
     5→## Installation
     7→```bash
     8→# with npm
     9→npm install @enclosed/crypto
    10→
    11→# with yarn
    12→yarn add @enclosed/crypto
    13→
    14→# with pnpm
    15→pnpm add @enclosed/crypto
    16→```
    17→
    18→## License
    20→This project is licensed under the Apache 2.0 License. See the [LICENSE](./LICENSE) file for more information.
    21→
